episodes.title: Shunned Amish Woman interview-Mary
episodes.description:
Soft White Underbelly interview and portrait of Mary, a woman who was shunned by her Amish community now living in Colorado.

For ad-free, uncensored videos and plenty of exclusive content please subscribe to the Soft White Underbelly subscription channel at softwhiteunderbelly.com. It's $10 a month and watchable on Apple and Android mobile apps, Roku TV, Apple TV and Amazon Fire.

Here's a link to a GoFundMe campaign to help some of the people seen in SWU interviews: https://gofund.me/9ebad507
